WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.564
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.564 --> 00:00:05.348
I just have a video I want to do for you all today.

00:00:05.799 --> 00:00:14.173
I've been praying and asking the Lord what he's wanting me to talk to you all about, and so I have a direction I think I need to go.

00:00:14.426 --> 00:00:18.559
The next two things I'm going to tell you about were open-eyed visions when I was praying.

00:00:18.559 --> 00:00:24.520
I was just praying, just like I am right here in this chair right now, and all of a sudden the Lord opened a portal above me.

00:00:24.520 --> 00:00:29.660
I saw a massive portal open because I just asked him, 'How's your day today, Lord?

00:00:30.150 --> 00:00:31.415
What were you about?

00:00:31.415 --> 00:00:32.342
What were you doing today?

00:00:32.342 --> 00:00:44.386
' I was just curious, just talking to him like I normally do, and all of a sudden he said, 'Brandon, I'll show you what I was doing,' and he opened up a banquet portal over my living room.

00:00:44.920 --> 00:00:55.046
I saw him—this is pretty cool—I saw him getting our table ready for our banquet.

00:00:55.046 --> 00:01:04.109
There were massive tables for a reception for us when we come home.

00:01:04.109 --> 00:01:10.660
Every plate was so perfect, but every plate was different.

00:01:11.175 --> 00:01:19.465
It was a flower, but my plate that was in front of me, he showed me in the spirit realm.

00:01:19.465 --> 00:01:23.480
I looked up and I could see the tables, and the plates were perfect.

00:01:23.480 --> 00:01:34.231
It was a perfect lily, but it was almost transparent; it was red and had all the beautiful designs on this plate.

00:01:34.587 --> 00:01:39.987
On the plate was a name card, and my name was written on the plate.

00:01:40.670 --> 00:01:49.292
It was a reserved seat for me for this banquet that we will partake in when the Rapture of the church happens.

00:01:51.100 --> 00:01:53.467
This is one of the first things that happens.

00:01:53.467 --> 00:01:57.124
I saw a banquet; he has a party for us.

00:01:57.124 --> 00:02:01.079
It is a massive celebration of us coming home.

00:02:01.679 --> 00:02:11.338
All of the plates were perfect, like I said, and then we had these glasses, and all the glasses were this fine crystal that I've never seen on this Earth before.

00:02:12.476 --> 00:02:19.857
The glasses were beautiful, and you could see the forks, and the forks were perfect.

00:02:19.857 --> 00:02:29.621
They had all the forks lined up, and they had a napkin and the plates and all the beautiful place setting.

00:02:32.870 --> 00:02:41.729
So everybody had—like I said, you could see the people that I was familiar with from this Earth that were my friends, the people that I know that are born again.

00:02:41.951 --> 00:02:55.347
My wife had her place next to me and other people that I love, family members and stuff, and they had their name tags in their reserved plate all around us.

00:02:56.236 --> 00:03:03.531
I could just see directly around me all the beautiful stuff, but everybody's stuff was personalized to them.

00:03:04.006 --> 00:03:13.185
It wasn't just like one type of plate or one type of glass; it was personalized to the desires of your heart, what was inside of you.

00:03:13.185 --> 00:03:14.964
It was beautiful what he had done.

00:03:15.267 --> 00:03:32.457
And the centers of the table were these flower arrangements that were the most beautiful flower arrangements—like, white, they were white-looking white roses—and they had this tulle.

00:03:34.870 --> 00:03:39.585
There was drapery all coming out of these trees.

00:03:39.585 --> 00:03:49.199
There were trees—like these huge, massive oak trees like you would see in Louisiana at those plantation houses.

00:03:49.199 --> 00:03:51.119
It was an outside area.

00:03:51.119 --> 00:03:56.940
It wasn't like a building or a palace-looking arrangement area.

00:03:56.940 --> 00:03:59.187
This reception is outside.

00:03:59.187 --> 00:04:07.320
There was green grass all around, there were beautiful trees all up, and they were covering on the top.

00:04:08.139 --> 00:04:16.254
There was drapery all coming down from these trees all underneath where the banquet's at.

00:04:16.519 --> 00:04:32.703
And there were these diamond-like beads, pearls; there were beautiful pearls hanging out of the trees, all fastened with the tulle, all this beautiful white silk, beautiful mesh.

00:04:33.309 --> 00:04:42.770
The pearls were wrapped in it; it was gold, and you could see all the colors.

00:04:44.720 --> 00:04:48.509
It was draped, and it was so decorated, so perfect.

00:04:48.509 --> 00:04:50.840
It was like a wedding reception.

00:04:52.489 --> 00:04:54.306
Everything was just immaculate, gorgeous.

00:04:55.132 --> 00:05:01.126
I try to capture and tell you everything the Lord showed me.

00:05:01.126 --> 00:05:12.604
This beautiful banquet had some kind of little lights; it sounds really weird, like twinkle lights inside of the tulle and the pearls.

00:05:15.840 --> 00:05:20.400
It was absolutely gorgeous.

00:05:20.400 --> 00:05:26.750
Everything—the place settings, the vases with flowers and everything—was so precious.

00:05:34.537 --> 00:05:34.914
This is his celebration for us when we come home.

00:05:34.914 --> 00:05:40.217
Then this is another time I'm praying; these are two different times I was praying.

00:05:41.070 --> 00:05:43.720
Again, I always ask the Lord, 'How's your day today?

00:05:44.697 --> 00:05:47.759
How are things going?

00:05:47.759 --> 00:05:53.239
' Just like I'm talking to a friend—he's my best friend—so it's like you're talking to your friend on the telephone.

00:05:53.639 --> 00:05:55.749
I always ask, 'Hey, how's your day today?

00:05:56.319 --> 00:05:57.990
What did you do today?

00:05:57.990 --> 00:06:04.930
' just like you talk to your wife or your husband to ask how their day was.

00:06:04.930 --> 00:06:09.980
So, I asked how his day was just like I did again, and I said, 'Lord, how was your day today?

00:06:09.980 --> 00:06:11.208
What all went on?

00:06:11.208 --> 00:06:15.168
' All of a sudden, he said, 'Hi, Brandon,' and he started talking to me again.

00:06:15.600 --> 00:06:22.173
He said, 'I want to show you what we're doing today,' what was going on in heaven.

00:06:22.546 --> 00:06:26.189
He said they're having a reception practice, a parade practice.

00:06:27.354 --> 00:06:40.696
He said, 'When you come home in the Rapture, son, we are going to have a massive homecoming party for you when you come into heaven.

00:06:40.696 --> 00:06:52.320
Everybody that has died before you, they're waiting for you, and we are going to celebrate all the people—this massive amount of the church that is coming home in the Rapture.

00:06:52.320 --> 00:06:55.919
' He said we're going to have a massive parade.

00:06:55.919 --> 00:07:01.559
It's a reception, but I could see the people, and they had banners.

00:07:04.200 --> 00:07:06.340
He showed me what they were doing.

00:07:08.126 --> 00:07:15.340
Jesus was riding a white horse, and he was the head of the reception that they were practicing.

00:07:15.720 --> 00:07:25.333
All the people kept saying, 'For the Lord is good and his mercy endureth forever,' as he was riding on this horse in heaven.

00:07:26.133 --> 00:07:27.839
I could see the streets of gold.

00:07:27.839 --> 00:07:36.759
I could see the people all on both sides of the streets, just like the Macy's Thanksgiving Day Parade.

00:07:37.584 --> 00:07:40.809
Both sides of the street had people all lined down.

00:07:40.809 --> 00:07:44.959
It looked like a massive town; it looked like a city.

00:07:44.959 --> 00:07:54.648
I could see buildings on both sides; there were massive buildings all beautifully designed, kind of like you would see in Europe.

00:07:54.648 --> 00:08:01.600
They had old English-style roofs with tile, and it was beautiful.

00:08:04.388 --> 00:08:09.520
There were buildings on both sides like a downtown area in heaven.

00:08:09.880 --> 00:08:16.560
I could see the people, and Jesus was riding on the gold street on his horse.

00:08:16.846 --> 00:08:24.270
People had those kingly banners that said 'King of Kings' and 'Lord of Lords.

00:08:24.270 --> 00:08:33.222
' All the banners were going down the street, and people had them like they were celebrating, like they were rejoicing.

00:08:33.222 --> 00:08:38.404
And this is going to sound really crazy, but there was confetti in the air.

00:08:38.404 --> 00:08:43.032
I could see gold confetti, and people were celebrating.

00:08:43.519 --> 00:08:52.360
They were practicing, getting ready for the coming of the church, the people that are on this earth, like a massive reception.

00:08:52.570 --> 00:08:57.462
You could see all this stuff going on, and he said, 'We're getting ready for you, son.

00:08:57.462 --> 00:08:59.540
We're getting ready for the church.

00:08:59.540 --> 00:09:04.897
' I got so excited because I could see all the people rejoicing.

00:09:06.451 --> 00:09:11.799
They kept saying, 'For he is good and his mercy endures forever.

00:09:11.799 --> 00:09:17.403
' I could hear all the people, and he was riding his horse.

00:09:17.848 --> 00:09:24.320
His horse had a bridle that had all these jewels on it.

00:09:24.320 --> 00:09:26.377
His horse was beautiful.

00:09:28.613 --> 00:09:39.519
The thing in the front of the horse had these beautiful diamonds and all these beautiful emerald-looking things, like sapphires and rubies.

00:09:40.664 --> 00:09:44.564
All this beautiful stuff was on the chest of the horse.

00:09:45.148 --> 00:09:50.476
He was riding his horse, and the horse was beautiful, going through the town.

00:09:51.418 --> 00:09:55.909
He was being worshiped in heaven, and the people just kept saying things like that.

00:09:55.909 --> 00:10:21.457
Jesus was in awe of how much he loves us, how much he cares, and all the personal detail he takes the time to love on His people.

00:10:31.720 --> 00:10:54.771
People have no idea how much Jesus loves you and how much he takes thought for every detail—from the plates to the forks to the parade.

00:10:54.771 --> 00:10:59.519
He's so excited for his children to come home.

00:10:59.519 --> 00:11:02.204
He's waiting on us.

00:11:02.204 --> 00:11:13.559
When God says, 'Go,' he's coming back for us, and we're going to rule and reign with him forever and ever.

00:11:13.559 --> 00:11:27.054
For the King, he is good; Jesus is good, and his mercy endures forever.

00:11:27.054 --> 00:11:34.735
There was a bridge with this huge river going through it.

00:11:34.735 --> 00:11:37.210
The town was right here.

00:11:38.936 --> 00:11:47.460
I could see as I was looking in, and the gold street was going over this bridge.

00:11:47.850 --> 00:11:54.784
There was a river going through heaven, this massive river, and the river was flowing.

00:11:54.784 --> 00:12:00.000
It was flowing out of the throne—living water.

00:12:00.000 --> 00:12:08.900
You could see that there were these steps that went up after this huge bridge over the river.

00:12:08.900 --> 00:12:12.347
There was green on both sides and, like I said, there was this town.

00:12:12.347 --> 00:12:17.500
I could see it, and there was this beautiful castle-looking thing.

00:12:18.020 --> 00:12:22.190
I don't even know what it was, but it was so beautiful.

00:12:22.190 --> 00:12:29.070
This massive castle-looking building was over here where he was riding his horse.

00:12:29.380 --> 00:12:32.640
All the people were there, and they had their gowns on.

00:12:32.920 --> 00:12:40.389
This is what's really amazing too: everybody that was worshiping him had different gowns.

00:12:40.389 --> 00:12:45.160
Not one gown was the same; not one robe was the same.

00:12:45.160 --> 00:12:47.072
You could see them, and they were beautiful.

00:12:47.072 --> 00:12:49.120
There were different colors.

00:12:49.120 --> 00:12:52.864
Everybody thinks it's just a white gown, but there were robes with colors.

00:12:55.307 --> 00:12:59.040
Like I said, there was no gown the same on these people.

00:12:59.040 --> 00:13:06.791
Some people had robes, some people had gowns, but there were more gowns than there were robes.

00:13:06.791 --> 00:13:17.171
It looked like there was a lot of people that just had a gown of salvation; they were born again, they had a revelation knowledge of just getting saved.

00:13:17.646 --> 00:13:31.120
The people who had robes had beautiful colors on these robes, and there were emblems and things of honor for what you did on the earth, what you did for him.

00:13:31.680 --> 00:13:40.199
It was beautiful, all the different stuff, and there were patches; they were thick, beautiful robes.

00:13:40.979 --> 00:13:46.280
I couldn't see the people's faces because they were all standing with their backs toward me.

00:13:52.124 --> 00:14:03.269
On the other side of the street, I could see the people a little bit, and they were all lining the streets.

00:14:03.279 --> 00:14:11.951
So, I look forward to it.

00:14:11.951 --> 00:14:23.734
I look forward to it—the peace, the presence.

00:14:23.734 --> 00:14:36.804
Oh Jesus, I take myself back when I talk about it; it's like I go back there.

00:14:36.804 --> 00:14:44.568
I can feel it, the feeling that I had whenever I could see him on his horse.

00:14:45.880 --> 00:14:51.845
When he was on his horse—I'll tell you what Jesus was wearing—he had a crown on.

00:14:52.290 --> 00:15:00.920
The crown was beautiful and towered above his head and had all kinds of really cool jewels and things on it.

00:15:00.920 --> 00:15:02.059
It was gorgeous.

00:15:02.059 --> 00:15:11.639
This crown was gorgeous, and it had this white banner around the bottom of it.

00:15:12.079 --> 00:15:20.059
It looked like it was purple and had all kinds of really cool stuff around the bottom of this crown, like fur.

00:15:22.480 --> 00:15:25.745
He had a cape on.

00:15:27.527 --> 00:15:39.308
When he was on his horse, he had this gold medallion thing in the middle, and his cape went back off of his body and draped down by his legs.

00:15:43.890 --> 00:15:46.519
Everything was just so perfect.

00:15:46.519 --> 00:15:49.253
So, Father, I thank you right now in the name of Jesus.

00:15:49.253 --> 00:16:03.062
I'm going to do a blanket prayer for all the people that have asked for help, all the prayer needs, all of the healings, and the people dying of a disease.

00:16:03.062 --> 00:16:08.959
For their loved ones who are far away from the Lord, Father, we thank you.

00:16:08.959 --> 00:16:21.980
Lord, you showed me in a vision today like little birds, and I said, 'Father, they're like little birds chirping in a mama's nest, and they're asking, "Help, help, help, cheep, cheep, cheep.

00:16:21.980 --> 00:16:28.319
"' I saw them in the spirit, Lord, and I said, 'God, there's so many mouths to feed.

00:16:35.191 --> 00:16:35.568
I can't do it all; I don't know what you want me to do.

00:16:35.568 --> 00:16:39.615
' And you said to me, 'It's my job, Brandon.

00:16:43.085 --> 00:16:43.940
The Holy Spirit will take care of this.

00:16:43.940 --> 00:16:50.866
' And I saw that big bird dump a whole bunch of worms on those little babies.

00:16:50.866 --> 00:16:59.992
Today I pray that for you: the Holy Spirit's going to meet your every need right where you're at.

00:17:04.749 --> 00:17:09.030
Jesus has got this for you.

00:17:13.805 --> 00:17:14.096
I call healing over your bodies, I call deliverance over you in Jesus' name.

00:17:30.050 --> 00:17:30.385
I call restoration over your marriages; you may be having marriage problems.

00:17:30.385 --> 00:17:33.360
I call restoration over your marriages in Jesus' name.

00:17:33.360 --> 00:17:37.880
I call blessing over your home in Jesus' name.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:09.800
Financially, I call it; that the Lord would bless you and keep you, may his face shine upon you and be gracious to you and give you peace.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
I call those blessings over their home in Jesus' name.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.400
And we praise the Lord for everything he's already done and what he continues to do in your life in the name of Jesus.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.650
Jesus loves you, and I love you, and I'm so thankful that you're a part of my family here.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
God bless you all.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Bye-bye.
